6)Select the total number of Employees in Communications departments

SELECT COUNT(name)as count FROM employee AS E INNER JOIN dept AS D ON D.dep_id = E.dep_id  WHERE dep_name = 'COMMUNICATIONS'
o/p:
COUNT
-----------
          6
